- `/private/var/folders/hh/3_hdf8cx5dl5hbp_gj4gzrqm0000gn/T/tmp.o4RqwYIjPs/tq-project/store/store.go` -- Event type, Watcher interface definition
- `/private/var/folders/hh/3_hdf8cx5dl5hbp_gj4gzrqm0000gn/T/tmp.o4RqwYIjPs/tq-project/store/memory.go` -- Subscriber management, Watch(), notify() implementation
