- `/private/var/folders/hh/3_hdf8cx5dl5hbp_gj4gzrqm0000gn/T/tmp.o4RqwYIjPs/tq-project/.claude/references/concurrency-patterns.md` -- Channel patterns and shutdown sequence reference

